### BillingService responsibilities

- validate billing period and units
- load applicable templates and charges
- build invoice lines
- persist `Invoice` + `InvoiceLine`
- optionally generate PDF/print output
- log audit entry

### PaymentService responsibilities

- validate payment metadata
- allocate amount across targets
- update invoice balance and arrears
- record allocations
- wrap all updates in a database transaction
- emit audit record

### ExpenseService responsibilities

- create/edit expense records
- manage approval workflow
- update payable/fund balances
- attach supporting documents
- notify approvers if needed

